Mixxx is designed for DJ'ing for both professional and semi-professional
users. Mixxx was started in early 2001 as one of the first digital DJ
systems.  Today Mixxx includes many features common to digital DJ solutions,
but also some very unique features: It is free, and runs on all major
desktop operating systems. Futhermore Mixxx has a number of key features to
help the DJ in the live mix: Beat estimation, parallel visual displays, and
support for many DJ input controllers.
